    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-02-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-02-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="1018"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1018">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Woodford</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-02-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 19, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 149.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Yesterday, the 18th instant, I had the honor to
                    telegraph the President as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p rend="right">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>, <hi rend="italic">February 18,
                                1898.</hi>
                        </p>
                        <p rend="flushleft">President <hi rend="smallcaps">McKinley</hi>, <hi
                                rend="italic">Washington:</hi>
                        </p>
                        <p>Her Majesty the Queen has just sent one of the gentlemen of the royal
                            household to express, through me to Your Excellency, her profound sorrow
                            and sympathy in the sad accident which has befallen the U. S. S. <hi
                                rend="italic">Maine</hi> at Habana.</p>
                        <p rend="right">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodford.</hi>
                        </p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>I have, etc.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stewart L. Woodford.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
